AcademicBackground
Dr.ChangjoinedtheInstituteofBiomedicalEngineeringatZhejiangUniversityin2013afterhecompletedhispost-doctoralpositionatOxfordUniversityin2012.BeforehestudiedhisPh.D.degreeatUniversityCollegeLondon(UCL)in2011,heservedasR&amp;DmanagerandprincipalinvestigatorforfiveyearsattheIndustrialTechnologyResearchInstitute(ITRI,Taiwan).Hehavepublishedover25scientificjournalsandbeengranted32internationalpatentsinthedevelopmentofflexible/rigidhealthcaredevicesforbiomedicalapplications,whichhavebeendirectlytransferredintoseveralindustrialsectors.Hispreviousawardsinclude2007BestInventionAwards,the2002PhiTauPhiPrize,2007ITRIEliteAward,the2007OutstandingResearchSilver-AwardandtheBestConferencePaperAwardfromtheASME,theprestigiousOverseaResearchScholarship(ORS)Award,theOSAAwardinboth2009and2010,etc.HealsoactsasamemberoftheFIT'sacademiccommitteeofZhejiangUniversityandamemberofOverseaHigh-levelTalentsofZhejiangProvince.Currently,heisworkingonsmartnewmaterialsandmethodologiestoengineernewmicro/nanostructuresforbiomedicalapplicationsandhealthcarepromotion.
